comment._content: The aircraft closest to the camera is a Stinson tri-motor...per the digitised newspapers, Airlines of Australia began operating several of these in 1936... nla.gov.au/nla.news-page9400817 Pic of VH-UQG over Brisbane in April 1936...possibly the same aircraft... nla.gov.au/nla.news-article36792167
